      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. While it is mechanically sound and has been well-maintained under the hood, the exterior does show its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a few small dings. The interior shows moderate wear, particularly on the driver's seat and floor mats, but remains functional and smoke-free. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who values performance and utility over a perfect cosmetic appearance.",
