    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s super reliable and ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s super comfy inside and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
