      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-overhead cam design with Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. This example is mechanically sound, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already performed and a recent valve shim adjustment to maintain the 8,000 RPM redline's integrity. The suspension architecture remains tight with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. Minor cosmetic wear consistent with mileage, but the drivetrain remains a benchmark of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Mechanically sound.",
      "price": 28500.0,
