    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and value, having been maintained with a focus on longevity. The exterior finish presents beautifully, retaining a high gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with well-preserved upholstery and carpets; all interior plastics and trim pieces are intact and free of cracks. Every feature, including the infotainment system, power seats, and ice-cold air conditioning, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefited by a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly through all gears, and is ready for immediate daily use without any looming maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, offering a distinguished combination of performance and reliability. This automobile has been curated to meet high standards of mechanical excellence and aesthetic appeal, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience. With a comprehensive service history and a well-preserved interior, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning professional seeking both value and quality.",
      "price": 34500.0,
