      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's been well-loved and still runs like a dream, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for a solid, reliable set of wheels that won't break the bank. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
